   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Ca s-l lege nu-ndrzneau.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Un btrn atuncea vine:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Dai frnghiile la mine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Mie zilele de-mi curm,</text:p>
